column2: J. Alexander's Holdings, Inc. owns and operates complementary upscale dining restaurant concepts. The company is headquartered in Nashville, Tennessee and currently employs 3,800 full-time employees. The firm is engaged in providing contemporary American cuisines. J. Alexander's is an upscale dining restaurant offering a contemporary American menu. J. Alexander's menu features rib of beef; hardwood-grilled steaks, seafood and chicken; pasta; salads; soups; and assorted sandwiches, appetizers and desserts. Stoney River's menu features its Coffee-Cured Filet Mignon made with select tenderloin, as well as other beef options. On Sundays, Redlands Grill offers a selection of made-from-scratch brunch items, including Belgian waffles, eggs benedict, huevos ranchero, quiche, omelettes, and lemon and ricotta hotcakes. The Redlands Grill on West End also has a wine program that offers over 35 wines by the glass and maintains over 140 bottles.
